Klaus Ethgen wrote:
[...]
> Is there any way to configure run-help to use "man git-add" when I press
> <ALT>-H in a line with "git add"?

If your zsh is new enough:

autoload -Uz run-help-git

That should be all to do the trick.

Regards, Frank

